sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant App as App Cliente
    participant Login as /auth/login
    participant Hosted as HostedAuthenticationAppService
    participant OAuthRepo as IOAuthClientRepository
    participant Master as SaasMasterDb
    participant Token as /api/auth/token
    participant Auth as AuthenticationAppService

    App->>App: Gerar state, nonce, code_verifier e code_challenge S256
    App-->>Browser: Redirect para /auth/login
    Browser->>Login: GET com tenant_id, client_id, redirect_uri, scope, state, nonce, code_challenge
    Login->>Hosted: StartAsync(HostedAuthorizationRequest)
    Hosted->>OAuthRepo: Buscar OAuthClient ativo no tenant
    OAuthRepo-->>Hosted: OAuthClient
    Hosted->>Hosted: Validar redirect_uri exato, scope e PKCE S256
    Hosted->>Master: Criar HostedAuthTransaction + HostedAuthSession
    Login-->>Browser: Renderizar login ou reutilizar lc_sso
    Browser->>Login: POST credenciais e 2FA quando necessário
    Login->>Hosted: LoginAsync / ConfirmTwoFactorAsync
    Hosted->>Master: Inserir AuthorizationCodeGrant com code hash
    Login-->>Browser: 302 redirect_uri?code&state
    Browser-->>App: Entregar code e state
    App->>App: Validar state
    App->>Token: POST grant_type=authorization_code + X-Tenant-Id + code_verifier
    Token->>Hosted: ExchangeAuthorizationCodeAsync
    Hosted->>Master: TryConsumeAsync(code hash + PKCE)
    Hosted->>Auth: IssueHostedIdentityTokenAsync(subjectId)
    Auth-->>App: access_token + refresh_token
